divs: Sighting DetailsAround noon on the 23rd of December, 2011, I noticed yet more parallel vapor (or chemical) trails over my house. i took photos from my rear yard as well as from the rear deck of my home. It wasn't until I pulled the photos into photoshop to create a pano shot from several photos that I noticed a shiny object in one of the photos. I zoomed in on what appears to be a double sphere shaped object. May be a plane but it left no "vapor" trail like all the other planes did that day. If it was a plane, it makes me wonder why other aircraft were leaving miles-long trails. I do not know how long it was there and can not estimate altitude. It appears as though it is a similar altitude as the trails but have no way to know for sure. For what it is worth, I don't get a lot of air traffic over my home and have a difficult time explaining 10's or 20's of vapor trails running perfectly parallel to each other. I am including the original shot which contained the UFO as well as a zoom of the same shot.
Summary: UFO in what I believe to be chemtrails
